@startuml seq_06_view_activity_history
title Sequence Diagram: UC-06 View Activity History

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Activity Controller" as Controller
participant "Activity Service" as Service
participant "Activity Repository" as Repo

User -> Frontend: (1.1) Open Activity History page
User -> Frontend: (2.1) Choose a page of history records
Frontend -> Controller: (2.2) GET /api/users/activity-history?page=1
Controller -> Service: (3.1) Validate authenticated user
Service -> Repo: (4.1) Fetch paginated post history
Repo --> Service: (4.2) List of records and pagination data

alt Records found
    Service --> Controller: (5.1) History data
    Controller --> Frontend: (5.2) 200 OK (data array)
    Frontend --> User: (7.1) Display activity list
else No records found
    Service --> Controller: (6.1) Empty list
    Controller --> Frontend: (6.2) 200 OK (empty array)
    Frontend --> User: (6.3) Display "No activity" state
end
@enduml
